of flames and spews hot ash like a miniature

00:03:39.340 --> 00:03:43.740
volcano. This gives a whole new meaning to
the term “Pie”-rotechnics, and this just

00:03:43.740 --> 00:03:47.380
might be the first dessert, that burns it’s
own calories.

